WEBVTT

00:04:28.802 --> 00:04:30.414
Lakini mwanahisabati akiniambia

00:04:30.438 --> 00:04:33.961
hio ukitoa mara tatu
ukitoa tatu ni tisa,

00:04:33.985 --> 00:04:38.854
hiyo ni aina ya mantiki inayoonekana
kama uaminifu.

00:04:40.674 --> 00:04:44.435
Tofauti ya maarifa, kwa maneno mengine,
sio lazima iwe ujinga.

00:04:44.948 --> 00:04:46.098
Inaweza ikawa mshangao.

00:04:46.482 --> 00:04:47.632
Au maajabu.

00:04:47.964 --> 00:04:49.147
Uwezekano.

00:04:49.894 --> 00:04:53.731
Na kwenye maisha yangu, nimegundua
ni vile nisivyovijua

00:04:53.755 --> 00:04:56.434
ndivyo ambavyo vimeninyanyua
na kunisukuma mbele zaidi

00:04:56.458 --> 00:04:59.026
kushinda vile ninavyovijua.